  <summary date="2019-08-28T12:47:31Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Agriculture Creates Real Employment Act or the ACRE Act

This bill reduces environmental requirements&#160;for agricultural producers,&#160;including requirements concerning

 the takings of certain birds&#160;at farms or aquaculture facilities, exports of certain sea urchins and sea cucumbers, discharges of pesticides, the use of information and data collected in accordance with certain environmental laws, or oil pollution on farms.</summary>
